---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import curiousAboutImage from '../../assets/images/mystery-box-overview/curious-about.png';
import whyMysteryBoxesImage from '../../assets/images/mystery-box-overview/why-mystery-boxes.png';
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center"
  aria-labelledby="mystery-box-overview-title"
>
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-8">
    <hgroup class="mx-auto text-center max-w-[49.375rem] w-full">
      <h2
        class="mb-2 font-sans font-bold text-[3rem] leading-[3.25rem] text-[#2D473E] text-balance"
        id="mystery-box-overview-title"
      >
        Top Tech Mystery Box at Unbeatable Prices
      </h2>
      <h3
        class="font-sans font-medium text-[1.25rem] leading-[1.465rem] text-[#006340]"
      >
        Fast shipping | Easy returns | Special discounts for students
      </h3>
    </hgroup>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <Image src={curiousAboutImage} alt="" loading="eager" />
      <article
        class="flex flex-col gap-6"
        aria-labelledby="mystery-box-overview-section-title"
      >
        <h4
          class="font-sans font-bold text-[2.625rem] leading-[3.25rem] text-[#2D473E]"
          id="mystery-box-overview-section-title"
        >
          Curious about the <strong class="text-[#006340]">StockX</strong> Mystery
          Box?
        </h4>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <p
            class="font-sans font-normal text-[1rem] leading-[1.5rem] text-[#293632]"
          >
            Experience the thrill of unboxing cutting-edge gadgets with Stockx
            Mystery Boxes. Each box is a treasure trove of high-quality
            electronics, handpicked to elevate your tech game.
          </p>
          <p
            class="font-sans font-normal text-[1rem] leading-[1.5rem] text-[#293632]"
          >
            Expect the unexpected! Our boxes are packed with the latest gadgets,
            from smartphones to gaming consoles, ensuring you get the best tech
            surprises every time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <article
        class="flex flex-col gap-6"
        aria-labelledby="mystery-box-overview-section-title"
      >
        <h4
          class="font-sans font-bold text-[2.625rem] leading-[3.25rem] text-[#2D473E]"
          id="mystery-box-overview-section-title"
        >
          Why is everyone buzzing about these boxes?
        </h4>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <p
            class="font-sans font-normal text-[1rem] leading-[1.5rem] text-[#293632]"
          >
            StockX Mystery Boxes are not just about products; theyâ€™re about the
            experience. Imagine the excitement of unveiling top-tier electronics
            at a fraction of the cost.
          </p>
          <p
            class="font-sans font-normal text-[1rem] leading-[1.5rem] text-[#293632]"
          >
            Our boxes include a variety of premium tech items, making it a
            must-have for every tech enthusiast. Join the buzz and see why
            everyone is raving about the unbeatable value and surprise factor of
            Stockx Mystery Boxes!
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <Image src={whyMysteryBoxesImage} alt="" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
